        "### Data Cleaning: Handling 'na' values and converting data types\n",
        "\n",
        "Many vacancy-related columns are currently of `object` type, likely due to 'na' values. Let's convert them to numeric, replacing 'na' with `NaN` for proper analysis. We'll also convert 'last_updated' to datetime."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
